name: House Plant #001
description:
The pandemic is forcing us to stay at home. 
a condition which initially is not very easy to get through it. 
seeking to avoid the bustle of the madness.

Growing plants at home is one thing that can be done. 
besides refreshing the eyes with its green color. 
Taking care every day like my own child is also entertainment in itself.
healing.
